enum Cursor {
  INHERIT = 'inherit',
  DEFAULT = 'default',
  POINTER = 'pointer',
  CROSSHAIR = 'crosshair',
  ROTATE = 'alias',
  MOVE = 'move',
  COL_RESIZE = 'col-resize',
  ROW_RESIZE = 'row-resize',
  EW_RESIZE = 'ew-resize',
  NS_RESIZE = 'ns-resize',
  NESW_RESIZE = 'nesw-resize',
  NWSE_RESIZE = 'nwse-resize',
  ZOOM_IN = 'zoom-in',
  ZOOM_OUT = 'zoom-out',
}

export default Cursor;
